title: Recap: Tech drops series to #1 Oklahoma - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech drops series to #1 Oklahoma - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – Texas Tech (19-18, 2-6) dropped game two and the series to No. 1 Oklahoma (35-0, 5-0) 11-0 in five innings Saturday at Rocky Johnson Field.
